#########
Noticed
#########

    plain ubuntu does not support project description

    project(friclient VERSION 1.0.0
            LANGUAGES C CXX
    )

#########
Solution
#########

    cmake 3.5, ubuntu default, does not support DESCRIPTION

#########
Noticed
#########

    in src/friUdpConnection.cpp, HAVE_SOCKLEN_T is not defined for ubuntu. Has to be set in cmake somehow

    #ifdef HAVE_SOCKLEN_T
        socklen_t sockAddrSize;
    #else
        int sockAddrSize;
    #endif

#########
Solution
#########

    Several compiler flags missing for ubuntu, how about windows?

    CFLAGS		   = -O2 -Wall \
                        -DHAVE_SOCKLEN_T \
                        -DPB_SYSTEM_HEADER=\"pb_syshdr.h\" \         # this line includes a custom header to nanopb/pb.h
                        -DPB_FIELD_16BIT \
                        -DHAVE_STDINT_H \
                        -DHAVE_STDDEF_H \
                        -DHAVE_STDBOOL_H \
                        -DHAVE_STDLIB_H \
                        -DHAVE_STRING_H 

    windows uses

    PB_SYSTEM_HEADER="pb_syshdr_win.h"                                # this line includes a custom header to nanopb/pb.h
    PB_FIELD_16BIT
    WIN32
    _DEBUG
    _LIB

    in the preprocessor definitions, that is it defines them.

#########
Noticed
#########

    Add -Wall flag to silence warnings, e.g. https://stackoverflow.com/questions/14231292/cmake-and-compiler-warnings

    if ( CMAKE_COMPILER_IS_GNUCC )
        target_compile_options(main PRIVATE "-Wall -Wextra")
    endif()
    if ( MSVC )
        target_compile_options(main PRIVATE "/W4")
    endif()

    not possible, however, maybe changes depending on compile flags, given by initial build strategy

#########
Noticed
#########

installed to /user/local

build with
cmake -DCMAKE_PREFIX_PATH='/usr/local' ..
make

execute with ./lbrjointsineoverlay

Network

System Settings -> Network -> Wired -> Options -> IPv4 Settings -> Address 172.31.1.148 Netmask 255.255.0.0


Build apps on windows

mkdir build && cd build
cmake -DCMAKE_PREFIX_PATH='C:\Program Files (x86)\FastRobotInterface' .. # on ubuntu /user/local
cmake --build . --config Release